<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么悟空不会帮我们？”马问八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23525</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说过，再也不要去找他帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23526</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>而且，我一直让师父念紧箍咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，那猴子一定非常讨厌我。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31957</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，这些都不重要了。”马说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须让悟空回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45781</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒犹豫了一会儿，跳上了一朵云飞走了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45782</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49236</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快他就到了花果山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49237</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看到悟空坐在巨大的瀑布旁边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他猴子都在附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们举着剑和矛，都安静地看着八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，悟空。”八戒说，“这山真美。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68846</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74061</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空皱起了眉头说：“你来干什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74062</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82723</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒看着地面。“师父希望你回去。”他嘟囔着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82724</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87726</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，对不起。”悟空说着站起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87727</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他让我走的。我绝对不会再帮他了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“回去吧，求你了。”八戒说，“我们都很想你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108861</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可不想你们。”悟空说，“你让师父念紧箍咒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108862</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112975</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我真想用金箍棒痛打你一顿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112976</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118586</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒勉强一笑。“我那只是开玩笑的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118587</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>123324</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我知道你是真的在保护师父。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>123325</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一点儿都不好笑。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127250</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137241</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的头真的很痛！”八戒开始哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137242</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143095</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“求你回去吧。师父遇上危险了，非常危险。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有个妖怪把他变成了老虎。悟净也被抓了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩说：“你就跟那妖怪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>孙悟空是你的朋友。他会害怕的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后就会放了你们所有人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我跟他说起过你的。”八戒撒谎说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”悟空靠近了一点，“他说什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172224</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175364</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒咬了一下嘴唇说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180549</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他大笑着说你只是个矮小的胆小鬼。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180550</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空的双眼燃起了怒火。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193158</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会为他说的话后悔的！八戒，我们走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193159</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪依然扮成了英俊的年轻人。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在桌前，正在和国王，王后吃饭。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个仆人走了进来，递了张纸条给他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看了纸条上的内容后，站起来说：</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很抱歉，陛下。我得走了。”他跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227978</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个仆人躲在柱子后面，看着年轻人离开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232655</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过，仆人变成了八戒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒咯咯直笑：“那妖怪会被吓一跳的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>年轻人跑了出去，变回了原样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跳到云上，快速飞回了宝塔那里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252258</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很着急，一路冲进了大门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252259</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当他看到百花公主的时候，松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，亲爱的！”他说，“我刚才非常担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我以为我永远失去你了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么会那么想呢？”公主问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪叹了口气说：“我收到了一张纸条。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275524</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>上面说有个猴子在这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他要毁了我的宝塔。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“之前是有个猴子来过。”公主说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？”妖怪说。他四下看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292198</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他没有毁了我的宝塔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292199</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他想要干什么？”公主犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300982</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道了肯定会不高兴的。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300983</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305516</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他把你之前抓住的那个和尚放走了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪看上去很生气。“他怎么敢......”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>315446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那猴子还做了点儿别的事情。”公主说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>315447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318391</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他做了什么？”妖怪问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318392</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>325156</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道光闪过。悟空突然站在了妖怪面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>325157</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>333191</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空微微一笑，说：“我把公主也放走了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>